```

## 4. No security middleware
Add the standard baseline:
- **`helmet()`** — sets secure HTTP headers (CSP, X-Frame-Options, HSTS, etc.).
- **`express-rate-limit`** — protects against brute-force/DoS.
- **`cors`** — explicit allow-list rather than default open.
- **`compression`** — optional, but be aware of BREACH if you serve secrets.

