There is no access log, so abuse or incidents cannot be reconstructed.

**Recommendation:**
```js
const morgan = require('morgan');
app.use(morgan('combined'));
```

### 8. No graceful shutdown (operational, minor)
SIGTERM will drop in-flight requests. Add a shutdown hook when you start handling real traffic.

```js
const server = app.listen(PORT, HOST, ...);
process.on('SIGTERM', () => server.close(() => process.exit(0)));
